details.description: Located in the thriving community of Ballantyne, our 2nd location in Charlotte blends neighborhood comfort with café sophistication. Inside, enjoy an expanded menu full of savory breakfast and lunch offerings plus baked goods, alongside freshly made donuts and specialty coffee. Sit back inside our bright dining room or soak up the sun in our expansive outdoor seating area. Whether you’re grabbing a midday bite between errands or lingering for a coffee chat, this location is built for both locals and visitors alike.

reviews_data.review_text: Charlotte donut guy here. Unfortunately the salty is extremely overrated and way overpriced. They have some fancy flavors just their efforts to charge more, but the quality is not there in these I hate to say.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Scott, we're so sorry to hear that you didn't enjoy your experience with us. Our donuts are made with a 24-hour brioche dough, giving them a unique texture and flavor compared to other shops. However, we always strive to improve and appreciate the feedback. We'd love for you to reach out to help@saltydonut.com so we can make things right. We hope you'll give us another chance to provide a better experience.

reviews_data.review_text: So excited that there’s a Salty in my neighborhood now! These are my favorite donuts ever. The flavors are unique and they pull them off so well. Whether you get something simple or go for a flavor that’s more complex (GF toasted banana milk really impressed me), I think you’ll be pleased. Also, try their coffee + lemonade…it’s one of the best I’ve ever had.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Kat, thank you so much for this incredible review! We're thrilled to hear you enjoyed our unique flavors and coffee lemonade. It's always a pleasure introducing our one-of-a-kind donuts to guests like yourself. We look forward to welcoming you back soon for another unforgettable experience!
